Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古手川
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了不讓你們玩得太過火來監視你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩人一起來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝點冰的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  古手川不去游泳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先把游泳圈吹起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你吹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用打氣筒的話還是很累的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  為什麼對我那麼溫柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.57,0:07:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這身泳衣是昨天菈菈同學邀請我去泳池時  匆忙間買的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不會覺得奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛  這小貓泳圈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  說得太曖昧了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小靜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  梨斗也跳下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈那傢伙  把我都拉到這地方來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結…結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.32,0:07:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗好帥啊  再跳一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊  明明跳得那麼帥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗你還真是變了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你變得能和穿著泳裝的女孩正常交流了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是沒刻意去看胸部這裡而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就算是這樣  要是以前的你的話早就暈過去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是因為受到和菈菈共同生活的影響吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人羨慕的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.51,0:08:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和菈菈的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到菈菈的影響…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:08:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是露恩和恭子的特別活動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家盡情燃燒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  露恩和恭子！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆發  要爆發了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請接受  我的激情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.84,0:09:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:09:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃  露恩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前一直對女孩子沒有免疫力的我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和喜歡的春菜一起來海邊和泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某種意義上來說這都靠菈菈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是這樣的哦  春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎菈菈同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.99,0:10:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是在為戀愛而煩惱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不嫌棄的話  我可以幫你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我還不太成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黏黏的啊  梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別發出這麼奇怪的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？梨斗  夢夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾克昂星系的原始生物水礦物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是非常稀有的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會在泳池裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來御門醫生的一位病人說他養的寵物逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.34,0:11:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字好像是叫露普爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把臉放在什麼地方啊！  禽獸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…  放我下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  別往奇怪的地方鑽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小闇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來不太想和蠕動的黏糊糊的對手打
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然液體生物再怎麼砍也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜  動物的話  你不能說服它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓它變聽話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  對方智力太低  根本就無法溝通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜被吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…  這下可是真的不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快退下  美柑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小闇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.91,0:12:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小闇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黏糊糊的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  連闇影也  這樣下去的話兩人肯定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.78,0:13:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先救誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起救
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.22,0:13:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  沒力氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但兩人都得救了  這樣就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  必須去救他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以  菈菈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在接近的話  又會被關進裡面的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果攻擊那傢伙身上的像是核的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:13:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定它會暈過去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:13:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小闇  拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須要去救梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家還真辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露普爾的主人來領取它了  大家放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是它本來的大小？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說和游泳池的水混合在一起引起了錯亂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是給人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.39,0:15:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒事了嗎  結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓我大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈  春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你們兩個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  剛才的風波也平息了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  是什麼呢  突然有話對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:16:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有發燒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…以前說過  還不清楚自己究竟是否喜歡菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然在我身邊時總讓我捏把汗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看到你的笑臉時  我感到很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  梨斗說喜歡我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝賀你  菈菈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等等  我還沒說完
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還有個從過去就一直喜歡的人在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？誰呢  是我認識的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.24,0:17:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為為…為什麼你會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是春菜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這反應…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼菈菈會說太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗說喜歡我  還說更喜歡春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究  究竟是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜也喜歡梨斗的事  不該由我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  梨斗  趕緊去向春菜告白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  趕快  趕快啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼突然變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果春菜也喜歡梨斗的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我和春菜就可以一起和你結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.21,0:17:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:18:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和菈菈和西連寺一起結婚？  是說一夫多妻制嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊  這種事在日本是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  佩凱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗大人和菈菈大人結婚  成為宇宙之王的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的規則就不用遵守了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太亂來了  想到哪裡就是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  裝備上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著春菜的方向  Let's  go
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇影
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對付你這種對手都要躲閃的話  簡直是奇恥大辱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就算是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也絕對不會容忍H的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這是…  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可抗力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多說無用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是倒大霉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦  結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露恩好像來了  正在找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家真厲害  剛才還那麼大的騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就平靜地玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.51,0:19:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君不顧一切來救我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.64,0:19:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈的話暫且放一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺現在能說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心意  長久以來的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西連寺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我有話想對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗和春菜兩個人單獨在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是機會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用念力將兩人緊靠在一起的話  肯定是不錯的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.15,0:20:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我  一直都
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗君是在這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡你！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:21:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？我…我？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.27,0:21:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大膽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗喜歡大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  梨斗和大家結婚的話  就會一直這樣熱鬧生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為  為什麼會變成這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭H
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我毫不在乎自己的位置哦  梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君  抱歉  突然泳衣就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.21,0:21:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.97,0:21:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜和梨斗和我  還有大家都一直在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也都一直這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.46,0:21:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣曲曲折折  梨斗麻煩多多的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(422,359)\fs21}ToLoveる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來還將會繼續下去
